sequenceDiagram
  participant Host as Host/IMC
  participant IPC as ipc_cmd_destory_stream
  participant B as bdma_exc_list
  participant TOP as TOP/HCQD regs
  participant U as CP User

  Host->>IPC: context_id, stream_id
  IPC->>IPC: mcqd_mask &= ~BIT(stream_id)
  IPC->>B: 查找正在执行的 task
  alt 找到执行中的 HCQD
    IPC->>TOP: 等 STOP_HCQDID 空闲
    IPC->>TOP: 写 STOP_HCQDID
    TOP-->>U: stop 请求
    U-->>TOP: CPE_FW_HCQD_STOPPED
    IPC->>TOP: release HCQD
    IPC->>TOP: clear release/stop/fw_stop
    IPC->>B: free task，清 task_valid
  end
  IPC-->>Host: DONE ACK
